latestPosts.caption:
Very rarely you get a client who trusts the vision with more than a 100% conviction . Thank you @shivanimodi_  for trusting us with your launch campaign. 

@devanshi.15 conceptualised this shoot which began with a song, onset of early Delhi winters, dreaming up a scene straight out of a movie.
Imagined an intimate musical evening inside a warm, jazz bar - where strangers gather, a band plays, and two lovers and ballroom performers take to the floor, lost in rhythm, and in each other.
Every character was sketched, shaped, styled and shot to play their part.
She wanted it to feel like a moment from a film — where you don’t just see the clothes, you feel the story.
Thank you to the most wonderful team for bringing this to life . 
.
.
